speaker: User
message: Hi, I am writing to ask if there is a potential soft block or issue with my student account? I am unable to use LawNet, cannot book facilities and face issues even with loading documents on Elearn sometimes. This has been going on for a while and usually there is an error message when I do these things. When I switch browsers to a private one (rather than my school account), the issue goes away.

speaker: User
message: Hi, this worked for me. Thank you~!

speaker: Help desk
message: Hello, how may I help you?

speaker: Help desk
message: Hi PERSON_FIRSTNAME_1, this is possible a cache/cookies problem, as the issue goes away when you switch to a a private browser. Clearing your cache/cookies should solve the issue. Here are some instructions:https://libfaq.smu.edu.sg/faq/266392

speaker: Help desk
message: No worries! Glad to hear that it worked :D
